; #DEFINE VIDEO50 ; Uncomment to Enable 50Hz Video Support (RTC)
;
; Rom Bug Fixes
; #DEFINE BUGFIX1  ; Uncomment to Fix Error 1 - 0573H - 32 Character Mode Line Length
